public abstract class PersistenceAnnotationBuilderProcessor<T extends com.foreach.across.modules.web.ui.ViewElementBuilder> extends Object implements EntityViewElementBuilderProcessor<T>
In case of a EntityPropertyDescriptor that has a PersistentProperty attribute, this processor will check and execute for the configured annotation types.
